data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a bonus converted garage, is located in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood. The home has been recently updated with new paint, flooring, and appliances. The kitchen features quartz countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet and a private bathroom. The backyard is fully fenced just done in 2021 and wonderful back with plenty space for fun and play. All impact windows and doors. The home is located close to schools, parks, and shopping. It is also close to major highways, making it easy to commute to work or school.
